natspec.author: Daccred.
natspec.details: The admin contract aims at taking all the deployer contracts       and mapping all the deployer function selectors to the respective        addresses, then in turn, calling the selectors via delegatecall       whenever the relevant deployment is needed.       In turn, whenever a new change is made to a contract, we can       easily, redeploy and remap.

addDeployerSelector(address,bytes4).details: This function adds a new selector or replaces a particular       selector from the selector map.

params._facet: Facet address containing the function we need.

deployERC721ExtensionCore(string,string).details: Deploys the ERC721ExtensionCore with a set name       and symbol using delegatecall to its facet.

deployERC721ExtensionSignature(string,st.details: Deploys the ERC721ExtensionSignature with its constructor       parameters using delegatecall to its facet.

deploySoulbound(string,string).details: Deploys the Soulbound Contract with a set name       and symbol using delegatecall to its facet.

deploySoulboundCore(string,string,addres.details: Deploys the SoulboundCore Contract with its constructor       parameters using delegatecall to its facet.

params._allowlistOwner: Desired owner of the contrat for sigs.

deploySoulboundRedeemable(string,string,.details: Deploys the SoulboundRedeemable Contract with its constructor       parameters using delegatecall to its facet.

params._allowlistOwner: Desired owner of the contrat for sigs.

deploySoulboundWithSignature(string,stri.details: Deploys the SoulboundWithSignature Contract with its constructor       parameters using delegatecall to its facet.

params._allowlistOwner: Desired owner of the contrat for sigs.

deployerSelectors.details: Mapping of all function signatures to the addresses.
